sources.title: Sunset Range
sources.description: Grant hides stolen money in the luggage of Bonnie Shea who is moving west. Later when he and his men arrive to retrieve the money, they also kidnap Bonnie. This sends Reasonin' Bates and his cowhands on their horses after the gangsters in their cars. You can find more information regarding this film on its IMDb page .

sources.title: Sunset Range (1935) HOOT GIBSON
sources.description:
Stars: Hoot Gibson, Mary Doran, James Eagles
 Director: Ray McCarey

 Grant hides stolen money in the luggage of Bonnie Shea who is moving west. Later when he and his men arrive to retrieve the money, they also kidnap Bonnie. This sends Reasonin' Bates and his cowhands on their horses after the gangsters in their cars.
